full_text: today at the chiropractor's office, Carry On Wayward Son started playing on the radio as I was lying facedown on the table waiting to be seen, and let me tell you, I went on a JOURNEY.

ah, Southern California: just had my white rideshare driver tell me the reason I can’t read in cars anymore is because of my imbalanced chakras and the fact that I’m no longer rooted in a sense of emotional community
